data.description:
Spacious Home in the heart of Gretna.  Large 3 bed|2bath|2419 SQ ft home with ceramic tile throughout, hardwood in bedrooms with separate den/living room. Bonus room great for home theater or gaming room with additional den or could turn into another bedroom  
fenced backyard.  With close distance of shopping centers, grocery stores, restaurants, schools, gas stations, highway and Downtown New Orleans.
